extendedInfo.description: If you are looking for attractions in Key West, Key West Mini Guide is right for you.Key West Mini Guide is your personal guide to help you explore the best attractions in Key West.We provide the list of best attractions in Key West here.In each attractions, it comes with detail and map.we also provide the search functionality for you to search the direction from your current location to the attractions that you're interested.The app will calculate and show the directions for you.In Attractions tab, all of the best attractions are here.In Map tab, you can see all of attractions on the map.****************************Main Features****************************- List of attractions- Detail and map on each attractions- Search direction- Search attractions- Map with all attractions****************************List of attractions****************************- Audubon House & Tropical Gardens- Bull & Whistle Bar- Captain Tony's Saloon- Danger Charters- Dry Tortugas National Park Ferry- Duval Street- Ernest Hemingway Museum- Fort Zachary Taylor Historic State Park- Harry S Truman Little White House- Hemingway House- Key West Aquarium- Key West Butterfly & Nature Conservatory- Key West City Cemetery- Key West Firehouse Museum- Key West Lighthouse Museum- Mallory Square- Nancy Forrester's Secret Garden- Red Barn Theatre- Smathers Beach- Southernmost Point in the Nation- The Studios of Key West- Tropic Cinema- Waterfront Playhouse
